{
  "stem": "1363.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the few synagogues where they went to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were yeshivas in our area as well, because we lived in a, let's say, the equivalent of Bondi here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a Jewish area, but it wasn't a typical-- the street where we lived, it wasn't a Jewish street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's only behind it was a Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if we wanted to, we did go to synagogues.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we, as I said, us ourselves were not religious in that respect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but there I don't remember having a Pesach or a Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Wunstorf.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, I don't know whether was that on purpose, or my parents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I haven't got any idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether they were afraid that-- of course by that time Hitler existed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And seeing that it was a Sudeten German township, they didn't want to rock the boat and tell everybody that we're Jewish, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really don't know, I mean.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not in Wunstorf-- in Budapest we were already with Jewish friends, yes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember that when we came back from that country boarding school into Budapest, we had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a housekeeper who was, naturally, Christian.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was very, very decent, our homekeeper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in the block of units, there was a caretaker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was a bit of a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a young son who took a fancy to me and I to him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that time, I was 13-- 12, 13, 14.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember that we had to hide in the elevator up and down to-- to steal a kiss here and there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] But he wasn't allowed to be seen with me, because I was Jewish and he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was back in Budapest, I would say in '40, '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
